{"tid":1685060,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Switch機主討論(128)| Luigi Mansion 3| 健身救世 | The Witcher 3|","createTime":"2019-10-31T11:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T00:59:40.000Z","uid":137912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5abbc3bc649699a39003348720d403af1e9b7fcd","tid":1685060,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:12:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">港版eShop只提供兌換功能</span></strong><br />\n買game要上 <a href=\"https://store.nintendo.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.nintendo.com.hk%2F&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=525fdcfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.nintendo.com.hk/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">帳號地區可隨時轉</span></strong>(Online會員地區亦會隨之變換) : <a href=\"https://accounts.nintendo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faccounts.nintendo.com%2F&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=3b1a74a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://accounts.nintendo.com/</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">___________________________</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">購買任何遊戲產品前請留意該產品於香港之代理商</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">/該店鋪之背景立場!</span></strong></span> <br />\n(見: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1565292/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1565292/page/1</a>)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">遊戲</span></strong>建議考慮於eShop購買<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">下載版</span></strong>遊戲 或 購買<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">水貨</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">主機</span></strong>方面<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">根據巴打報料</span></strong>大型連鎖電器鋪同日本百貨(如豐澤/百老匯/Aeon/Sogo/Uny..)嘅主機係直接同任天堂拎貨, 唔經代理, <ins><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">歡迎各位巴絲進一步提供/確認相關資料</span></strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">新垣結衣</span></strong>代言廣告公開!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 健身RPG</span></strong>「<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">健身環大冒險</span></strong>」10月18日發售<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s7iV4_w9hXo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds7iV4_w9hXo&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=8d871a4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s7iV4_w9hXo</a><br />\n<br />\n介紹影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wvHELogbm2E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwvHELogbm2E&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=a85b1750\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wvHELogbm2E</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ring/assets_top/img/header/hero03_pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.co.jp%2Fring%2Fassets_top%2Fimg%2Fheader%2Fhero03_pc.jpg&h=1e71b750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ring/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.co.jp%2Fring%2F&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=708a5cfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ring/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">買券換game! </span></span></strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Online會員限定</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">下載版遊戲優惠!</span></strong><br />\n9980YEN/99USD 2張下載版遊戲(任記/任記發行遊戲)換購券<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzWSCcF3AM8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDzWSCcF3AM8&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=04dfde57\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzWSCcF3AM8</a><br />\n<br />\n美區購買期限已過,<br />\n日區似乎無限購買時間, <br />\n雙區換購券皆需於購買後一年內使用<br />\n港區並無推出是次優惠<br />\n<br />\n可換購遊戲會隨新遊戲上市而增加<br />\n無限制購買次數, 但同時只可持有8張換購券</div><br />\n<br />\n美區: <a href=\"https://ec.nintendo.com/US/en/pretickets/70020000000061\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.nintendo.com%2FUS%2Fen%2Fpretickets%2F70020000000061&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=018c9d8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.nintendo.com/US/en/pretickets/70020000000061</a><br />\n日區: <a href=\"https://ec.nintendo.com/JP/ja/pretickets/70020000000021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.nintendo.com%2FJP%2Fja%2Fpretickets%2F70020000000021&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=7c1ca03a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.nintendo.com/JP/ja/pretickets/70020000000021</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * </div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  頭post包含 <span style=\"color: gold;\">Q&amp;A</span> / <span style=\"color: orange;\">實用資訊</span> / <span style=\"color: gold;\">遊戲發售表</span>, 請多加善用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"d449dc52e6ff365150815e71d955ad9b7fbc05aa","tid":1685060,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:13:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  頭post包含 <span style=\"color: gold;\">Q&amp;A</span> / <span style=\"color: orange;\">實用資訊</span> / <span style=\"color: gold;\">遊戲發售表</span>, 請多加善用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/xqr3LCfb/v1074002259-f46c3w132.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fxqr3LCfb%2Fv1074002259-f46c3w132.png&h=8e18177f&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>常見問題</strong></span></span></div><br />\n <br />\nQ: Switch有無鎖區?<br />\nA: 無，eShop地區跟 ac，一機可同時登入 8 個 ac <br />\n <br />\nQ: JoyCon 連接有問題/ 用用下無反應?<br />\nA: 可以試下撳實JoyCon側邊個Sync掣2秒<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點揀叉電器/USB-C 線?<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5oXEONa.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5oXEONa.png&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=8ecf31fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/5oXEONa.png</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: JoyCon手帶調轉插點算?<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7bfhKo7dqIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7bfhKo7dqIo&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=38711ee9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7bfhKo7dqIo</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: 點連 5gHz WiFi?<br />\nA: Set 個WiFi Channel去36-64 或 100-140之間<br />\n <br />\nQ: 連唔連到大學WiFi?<br />\nA: 連唔到<br />\n<br />\nQ: 部機黑畫面/定咗格/撳電源掣冇反應<br />\nA: 長撳開關掣十二秒<br />\n <br />\nQ: 要keep咩先有保養?<br />\nA: 1. 需維修的主機及配件 2. 主機外箱  3. 印有銷售店舖名稱或蓋印之購買收據 4. 主機包裝內之香港原裝行貨保固證 <a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Frepair.html&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=7e7c3017\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: Switch行版/日版/美版有咩分別?<br />\nA: 行版有保養同香港用嘅三腳火牛(不過任何版本都係用國際牛)，其他一樣，內置多國語言(無中文)<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Nintendo Switch</strong></span> 2017年3月3日 於香港正式發售<br />\n售價 港幣$2,340<br />\n<br />\n任天堂Switch香港官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2F&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=575e7e4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂Switch Online App開放下載</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFELfwUXYAUv_l8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFELfwUXYAUv_l8.jpg&h=467237b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApp功能<br />\n1.同唔同遊戲會有連動要素, 例如Splatoon2, 透過個app可以睇到自己嘅對戰相關數據同買裝<br />\n2. 可以進行語音通話<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFGMQiBUMAAJRz2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFGMQiBUMAAJRz2.jpg&h=91a4ea8a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂Switch ONLINE會員服務</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DcowGUlU0AAFdUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDcowGUlU0AAFdUD.jpg&h=fa2640fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/onlineservice/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fhardware%2Fswitch%2Fonlineservice%2F&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=5ac80a04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/onlineservice/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">1. 網絡連線<br />\n<blockquote>成為收費會員後即可在Splatoon, Mario Kart等遊戲中享受網絡對戰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2. NES - Nintendo Switch Online<br />\n<blockquote>(類似Netflix)成為收費會員後即可享受20款<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>追加網絡連線功能</strong></span>嘅NES經典作品, 會定期追加新遊戲 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3. Cloud Save<br />\n<blockquote>成為收費會員後可備份存檔至雲端網絡, 部分遊戲為保公平(官方講法)並不對應cloud save </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4. Switch Online App<br />\n<blockquote> 連動電話app </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5. 特別優惠<br />\n<blockquote>成為收費會員後可享受不同優惠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會員可下載免費遊戲「<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Tetris 99</strong></span>」(俄羅斯方塊大逃殺)<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DzUa7NSUUAApUc-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDzUa7NSUUAApUc-.jpg&h=e10503d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DzVPftBWoAABC4-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDzVPftBWoAABC4-.jpg&h=0987c263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收費: <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每年</span> 港幣$155<br />\n可只購買1或3個月會員資格, 惟其價格亦較昂貴<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Nintendo Switch家長監護程式</span></strong></span><br />\n*裝左可以睇返自已玩左幾耐<br />\nAndroid:<a href=\"http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znma\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nintendo.znma&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=cfbdc0b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znma</a><br />\niOS:<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1190074407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fid1190074407&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=5575b4b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1190074407</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">任天堂會員 - MyNintendo</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://my.nintendo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmy.nintendo.com%2F&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=649eb4ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://my.nintendo.com/</a><br />\n<br />\